msgid ""
"Seven worked solid-mechanics examples in ``examples/solid/``, walking "
"from textbook linear elasticity all the way through hyperelasticity, "
"contact, plasticity, and a full paper-grade dataset suite. The examples "
"cover the three solver patterns TensorMesh supports for solid problems:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:10
#: 285073bd632e4d849b7eddb248efe81e
msgid ""
"**Direct linear solve** for small-strain linear elasticity "
"(``cantilever_beam``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:12
#: 8bfd2d701f4a4bd9855b6e0033afcf81
msgid ""
"**LBFGS energy minimization** for nonlinear problems where the potential "
"energy is well-defined: hyperelasticity, contact, plasticity "
"(``hyperelastic_beam``, ``hertzian_contact``, ``plasticity_*``, "
"``emmentaler``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/index.rst:16
#: 54fc616a146444b099ebb9eed2f7e22a
msgid ""
"**Multi-phase / staggered solvers** for problems where the energy depends"
" on auxiliary fields (``emmentaler`` phase-field, ``mousavi2026`` dataset"
" suite)."
msgstr ""

